	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The size of you mana pool does not matter really. You will always have enough for charming.<br><br>The trouble with mana and bard (and its not a trouble its intentional) is the regen rate of this mana. It is slow and NOTHING can speed it up.<br><br>So NEVER bother with wis / int / mana.<br><br>Concentrate on DEX STA AGI STR and CHA<br>DEX to reduce missed notes<br>STA to have more hps and to be able to fight longer<br>AGI to increase your defense (you ll need it when you will do crowd control)<br>STR is obvious for damage<br>CHA for charming and mezzing<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
