	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay, I've been playing for sometime now, but since the macro ability has been available, I have not used it, but I'm interested in how you might have setup your macros (i.e. cast 1, pause 30, etc.. ) .&nbsp;&nbsp;Please post if you know how to create a macro that will fit in at least 3 to 4 songs in one macro (not sure if it's possible, but would really like to know).<br><br> Sol<br> 56 Bard<br> Erollisi Marr<br>&nbsp;<br>Sol<br>58 Bard (Retired)<br>65 Feral Lord (Retired)<br>Maelin Starpyre</td></tr>
