	   <tr><td colspan=2>Is there a way to hot-key my instruments so I don't have to go open my inventory screen when I want to equip them? Any tips would be appreciated)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
