	   <tr><td colspan=2>Maximum SUSTAINABLE weave is three of the standard 3 tick songs....you can get four going part of the time, even maybe 2/3 of the time because casting time is 4 secs and tick is 6 sec's so 3 ticks x 6 secs gives you an 18 sec window. If you sing at the right portion of the tick, you can get 4 going but not sustain them indefinitely.<br><br>There is even less success when lag, stuns, missed note's comes into effet.<br><br>With the longer songs (selos 49) amp (30) you can actually weave 6. But 3 is the standard for 3 tick songs.<br>&nbsp;<br>Baron Nesoohc Tsal, the Rathe<br>Bard of the 56th Verse<br>(alts Fixem 21 Cleric Fletchum 21 Ranger)<br>Bhandade 22th season Cleric...FV<br>Natturally 22th season Ranger</td></tr>
