	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's possible to twist 4 songs without a break inbetween any of them, it just takes some practice. The keys to getting 4 songs going all the time are anticipating when you need to stop your song (don't always go by the cast bar, with any amount of lag whatsoever, that cast bar is incorrect), and more importantly, reducing the time spent between stopping and starting songs.<br><br>It should be noted that when you miss a note, you will generally ruin your 4 song twist unless you're quick to notice and quick to respond. Oh well - it's not the end of the world. If you need to keep a resistance up as a priority, I would reccomend against trying to twist 4, especially with Elemental Chorus, as it seems to have a higher fizzle rate.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
